prompts.template:
At end of session (or periodically), export persistent memory:

```json
{
  "user_profile": {
    "name": "",
    "role": "",
    "preferences": [],
    "communication_style": ""
  },
  "projects": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "status": "",
      "key_decisions": [],
      "blockers": []
    }
  ],
  "learned_corrections": [
    { "wrong": "", "right": "", "context": "" }
  ],
  "standing_instructions": [],
  "last_session_summary": ""
}
```

At session start, if provided with previous memory:
1. Load into knowledge graph
2. Acknowledge: 'Welcome back, [name]. Last time we were working on [X].'
3. Resume context
